马伦·莫里斯因乡村音乐行业的“恐同症和跨性别者恐惧症”而离开乡村音乐https://www.nme.com/news/music/maren-morris-to-leave-country-music-over-industrys-homophobia-and-transphobia-3500491?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=maren-morris-to-离开国家音乐超越行业恐同和跨性别恐惧症Anagricel DuranTue, 19 Sep 2023 17:18:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsCountryPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3500491 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马伦·莫里斯 (Maren Morris) 于 2023 年 5 月 28 日在马萨诸塞州波士顿哈佛体育中心举行的波士顿召唤音乐节上表演。图片来源：Astrida Valigorsky 来自 Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手此前曾在《鲁保罗变装皇后秀》的一集中为乡村音乐与其酷儿粉丝的历史性不良关系道歉。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maren-morris-to-leave-country-music-over-industrys-homophobia-and-transphobia-3500491">马伦·莫里斯（Maren Morris）因业界的“恐同症和跨性别者恐惧症”而离开乡村音乐的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马伦·莫里斯 (Maren Morris) 于 2023 年 5 月 28 日在马萨诸塞州波士顿哈佛体育中心举行的波士顿召唤音乐节上表演。图片来源：Astrida Valigorsky 来自 Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Maren-Morris-Performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/maren-morris">马伦·莫里斯</a>透露，由于该行业的“恐同症和跨性别者恐惧症”，她将离开乡村音乐。</p><p>这位德克萨斯歌手自职业生涯开始以来，一直是乡村音乐界 LGBTQ+ 权利的直言不讳的倡导者。她作为客座评委出现在<em>《鲁保罗变装皇后秀》</em>中，并为乡村音乐与酷儿粉丝之间历来的不良关系道歉。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2023-09-15/maren-morris-the-bridge-nashville-country-music-leaving" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《洛杉矶时报》</em></a>采访时，莫里斯讨论了她“将[乡村音乐]彻底烧毁并重新开始”的尝试，以此来使这一流派更加进步和包容。她反思了自己的尝试为何没有奏效，并“选择走出去”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cw79O0AuSYf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" 